OL,3,CMedical restrictions for driving
OL,4,Clicences toughened up in Jersey
OL,6,FDrivers of minibuses, coaches and
OL,7,Flarger vans in Jersey may need a
OL,8,Fmedical certificate to prove they are
OL,9,Ffit enough to be on the road from
OL,10,FOctober.
OL,12,FRules are being tightened to bring the
OL,13,Fisland closer in line with EU and UK
OL,14,Flaw, the government has confirmed.
OL,16,FAnyone who first applies for a 'Group
OL,17,F2' licence, which is needed to operate
OL,18,Flarger vehicles, will have to submit a
OL,19,Fmedical certificate.
