OL,3,CMedical restrictions for driving
OL,4,Clicences toughened up in Jersey
OL,6,FThis document is also needed when a
OL,7,Fdriver starts suffering from some
OL,8,Fconditions and for any motorists aged
OL,9,F45 or over when they renew their
OL,10,F'Group 2' licence.
OL,12,FTo receive a medical certificate for
OL,13,Fthis type of licence, drivers must
OL,14,Fprove they have not had a seizure or
OL,15,Ftaken prescribed medication to treat
OL,16,Fepilepsy in the last five years, and
OL,17,Fthey have not had two or more seizures
OL,18,Fin the last 10 years.
