OL,3,CMedical restrictions for driving
OL,4,Clicences toughened up in Jersey
OL,6,FThese motorists also need a medical
OL,7,Fexamination by a specialist in
OL,8,Fneurology who deems they are healthy
OL,9,Fenough to get behind the wheel.
OL,11,FOther requirements include the ability
OL,12,Fto read a number plate from 20 metres
OL,13,Fand reach the new field of vision and
OL,14,Fvisual acuity standards - someone who
OL,15,Fcan only see with one eye will not be
OL,16,Fable to hold a 'Group 2' licence.
OL,18,FAnyone with diabetes who is treated
OL,19,Fwith insulin or another hypoglycaemic
OL,20,Fdrug must also meet new rules.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
