OL,3,CMedical restrictions for driving
OL,4,Clicences toughened up in Jersey
OL,6,FThere are separate requirements for a
OL,7,F'Group 1' licence, needed to drive
OL,8,Fsmaller vehicles such as cars,
OL,9,Falthough these standards have largely
OL,10,Fstayed the same.
OL,12,FDrivers with concerns about how the
OL,13,Fnew restrictions could affect them
OL,14,Fshould speak to their doctor.
OL,16,F'Group 1' licences will last for 10
OL,17,Fyears with 'Group 2' ones being valid
OL,18,Ffor five years from the age of 45 and
OL,19,Fone year from the age of 65.
